\c 15
\s Vatumwa vanomwe vane ndiro nomwe
\p
\v 1 Zvino ndakavona chimwe chiratidzo kudenga, chikuru uye chinoshamisa: Vatumwa vanomwe vane matambudziko manomwe ekupedzisira, nekuti kutsamwa kwaMwari kwakapedzeredzwa maari.
\v 2 Ndikaona chakaita segungwa regirazi rakavhenganiswa nemoto, naivo vawana kukunda chikara nemufananidzo wacho, nemucherechedzo nenhamba* yezita racho vamire pamusoro pegungwa regirazi vane udimbwa hwaMwari.
\v 3 Vakaimba rwiyo rwaMozisi muranda waMwari, nerwiyo rweGwayana vachiti: Makuru uye anoshamisa mabasa enyu, Ishe Mwari Wemasimbaose; dzakarurama uye ndedzechokwadi nzira dzenyu, imwi Ishe wevatsvene.
\v 4 Ndiani ungarega kukutyai, Ishe, nekukudza zita renyu? Nekuti ndimwi moga mutsvene; nekuti marudzi ose achauya achinamata pamberi penyu; nekuti zviito zvenyu zvakarurama zvakaratidzwa.
\v 5 Zvino shure kweizvozvo ndakaona, zvino tarira, yakazarurwa tembere yetende reuchapupu mukudenga;
\v 6 zvino kwakabuda mutembere vatumwa vanomwe vane matambudziko manomwe, vakafuka rineni yakachena inopenya, vakasungwa pazvifuva zvavo nemabhanhire endarama.
\v 7 Uye chimwe chezvisikwa zvipenyu zvina chakapa kuvatumwa vanomwe ndiro nomwe dzendarama dzizere nehasha dzaMwari, \add iye\add* mupenyu kusvikira rinhi narinhi.
\v 8 Tembere ikazadzwa neutsi hwunobva pakubwinya kwaMwari nepasimba rake; kukasava nemunhu wakagona kupinda mutembere, kusvikira matambudziko manomwe evatumwa vanomwe apera.
